    <item>
      <title>共和党议员就报告向马克·罗宾逊施压</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/mark-robinson-black-nazi-report-brings-pressure-from-republican-senators</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，共和党参议员对北卡罗来纳州共和党州长候选人马克·罗宾逊（Mark Robinson）的严厉报道表示担忧，并承认对唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）青睐的候选人提出了严重指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/mark-robinson-black-nazi-report-brings-pressure-from-republican-senators</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 16:51:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>舒尔茨领导的政党在德国州选举中领先于极右翼</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/scholz-s-spd-leads-in-brandenburg-state-vote-ahead-of-far-right</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的社会民主党似乎抵挡住了极右翼德国选择党的强劲挑战，保住了东部勃兰登堡地区的权力，使总理和他的政党避免再次遭遇令人尴尬的选举挫折。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/scholz-s-spd-leads-in-brandenburg-state-vote-ahead-of-far-right</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 16:07:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哈里斯在两项民意调查中表现出强劲势头，而摇摆州的势头依然强劲</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/harris-shows-momentum-in-two-polls-while-swing-states-stay-tight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日发布的两项全国登记选民民意调查显示，副总统卡马拉·哈里斯领先于唐纳德·特朗普，凸显了她在美国总统候选人努力争取支持率的同时，在多个州开始提前投票之际的强劲势头。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/harris-shows-momentum-in-two-polls-while-swing-states-stay-tight</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 15:45:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>乌克兰等待导弹决策，英国敦促西方保持“坚韧”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/uk-urges-western-fortitude-as-ukraine-awaits-missiles-decision</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国外交大臣戴维·拉米呼吁盟友在支持乌克兰时表现出“毅力”，他试图淡化因俄罗斯即将允许乌克兰在俄罗斯境内使用西方武器而导致的局势升级的威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/uk-urges-western-fortitude-as-ukraine-awaits-missiles-decision</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 15:16:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯里兰卡左翼政党誓言调整国际货币基金组织协议后赢得大选</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/sri-lanka-leftist-wins-presidency-after-vowing-to-rejig-imf-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[斯里兰卡的左翼候选人赢得了一场竞争激烈的总统选举，选民们因为该国陷入危机的两年间所遭受的经济痛苦而将现任总统赶下台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/sri-lanka-leftist-wins-presidency-after-vowing-to-rejig-imf-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 14:18:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>反对者提出谴责议案，法国政府面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/france-s-government-is-at-risk-as-opponents-eye-a-censure-motion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统埃马纽埃尔·马克龙的新政府立即引起各政治派别的愤怒反应，增加了政府迅速垮台的风险，这将进一步给法国紧张的公共财政前景蒙上阴影。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/france-s-government-is-at-risk-as-opponents-eye-a-censure-motion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 10:52:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞士选民否决政府养老金改革方案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/swiss-voters-shoot-down-government-s-pension-fund-reform</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士选民否决了政府的一项企业养老金改革计划，这是今年第二次在公民投票中否决该国退休制度适应人口结构变化的提议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/swiss-voters-shoot-down-government-s-pension-fund-reform</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 10:05:18 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>真主党回应传呼机攻击 以色列北部成为攻击目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/israel-s-north-under-fire-as-hezbollah-responds-to-pager-attacks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周日，以色列和真主党之间的交火和言辞冲突愈演愈烈，总部位于黎巴嫩的真主党向以色列北部大片地区发射了大约 115 枚火箭弹、导弹和无人机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/israel-s-north-under-fire-as-hezbollah-responds-to-pager-attacks</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 07:56:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿拉巴马州警方称伯明翰深夜枪击事件造成四人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/4-killed-in-late-night-shooting-in-birmingham-alabama-police-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉巴马州伯明翰（美联社）——警方周日称，阿拉巴马州伯明翰一个夜生活丰富的地方发生大规模枪击事件，造成 4 人死亡，17 人受伤，许多受害者被困在交火中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/4-killed-in-late-night-shooting-in-birmingham-alabama-police-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 07:25:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
